Problem -1: OPENCV-python HEADLESS ISSUES[RARELY SEEN, WHILE RUNNING AFTER MANY DAYS IF DEPENDNCY OR ENVIRONMENT IS CHANGED]

    You need to reinstall OpenCV with GUI (GTK) support:

    Install dependencies:

    sudo apt update
    sudo apt install libgtk2.0-dev pkg-config

    pip uninstall opencv-python opencv-python-headless
    pip install opencv-python

